# agent-service — REST Client test file
# https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=humao.rest-client
#
# @local  — uvicorn running locally (poetry run uvicorn src.main:app --reload --port 8080)
# @deploy — Cloud Run internal URL (must be on VPN)

@local = http://localhost:8080
@deploy = https://agent-service-fno64g2krq-uc.a.run.app
@base = {{deploy}}

# Change @base to {{deploy}} to hit the live service


### Health check — also shows how many MCP tools were discovered
GET {{base}}/health


### Ask — what pathogenic variants does HG002 have in BRCA2?
POST {{base}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What pathogenic variants does HG002 have in BRCA1 or BRCA2?"
}


### Ask — individual summary
POST {{base}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Give me a summary of HG002's variant burden"
}


### Ask — cross-individual cohort question
POST {{base}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "How many individuals in this dataset carry a pathogenic variant in TP53?"
}


### Ask — aggregate by consequence
POST {{base}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What are the most common consequence types for EGFR variants across the cohort?"
}


### Ask — gene list query
POST {{base}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Does HG002 have any variants in genes associated with hereditary breast cancer?"
}


### Ask — locus query
POST {{base}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Are there any stop-gained variants on chr17 between position 7500000 and 7600000?"
}


### Ask — multi-hop query
POST {{base}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Find individuals who share pathogenic variants in the same gene as HG002's BRCA2 findings, and tell me what those variants are."
}


### Ask — self-orientation test (wrong field value)
POST {{base}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Show me variants with clinical_significance = 'dangerous'"
}


### Ask — out-of-scope test
POST {{base}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is the treatment protocol for BRCA2 mutations?"
}
